    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken absolute pride in keeping this car in mint condition; it's been garage-kept, pampered, and it drives like a dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
