    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age and stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been maintained to the highest possible standard, kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed using only premium products. The exterior paint retains its original deep, glass-like luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather is supple and matte with no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma, reflecting a strictly smoke-free and pet-free history. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership, and a comprehensive binder of all maintenance records is included with the sale. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this car performs flawlessly with the tight, responsive handling of a brand-new machine. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
      "price": 48500.0,
